<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Return Policy</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>

<style>
  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

body {
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 50px auto;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

header,
footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
    background-color: #f1f1f1;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    border-radius: 8px;
}

header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5em;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: #2c3e50;
}

header p {
    font-size: 1.2em;
    color: #7f8c8d;
}

section {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
}

section h2 {
    font-size: 2em;
    color: #2c3e50;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e74c3c;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.subsection {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding-left: 20px;
    border-left: 3px solid #e74c3c;
}

.subsection h3 {
    font-size: 1.5em;
    color: #e74c3c;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.subsection p,
.subsection ul {
    font-size: 1em;
    color: #34495e;
}

.subsection ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
    margin-left: 20px;
}

.subsection ul li {
    margin-bottom: 5px;
}

footer p {
    font-size: 1em;
    color: #7f8c8d;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .container {
        margin: 20px;
        padding: 15px;
    }

    header h1 {
        font-size: 2em;
    }

    section h2 {
        font-size: 1.5em;
    }

    .subsection h3 {
        font-size: 1.2em;
    }
}

</style>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Return Policy</h1>
            <p>Our aim is to ensure you are completely satisfied with your purchase. If you are not satisfied, we're here to help.</p>
        </header>

        <section>
            <h2>1. Clear Return Policy</h2>
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Time Frame</h3>
                <p>Customers have <strong>30 days</strong> from the date of delivery to request a return.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Condition of Items</h3>
                <p>Items must be returned in their <strong>original condition</strong>, unused, and in the original packaging.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Non-Returnable Items</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Gift cards</li>
                    <li>Downloadable software products</li>
                    <li>Personal care items</li>
                    <li>Final sale merchandise</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>2. Return Reasons</h2>
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Options for Selection</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Item arrived damaged</li>
                    <li>Wrong item received</li>
                    <li>Item not as described</li>
                    <li>Better price available elsewhere</li>
                    <li>Changed my mind</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Custom Input</h3>
                <p>Customers can provide additional details about their return reason in a comment box during the return request process.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>3. Return Process</h2>
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Initiation</h3>
                <p>To initiate a return, log in to your account, navigate to your orders, and select the item you wish to return.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Return Label</h3>
                <p>Once the return is approved, a prepaid return shipping label will be provided via email.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Shipping Costs</h3>
                <p>Return shipping costs are <strong>covered by us</strong> for defective or incorrect items. For other returns, the shipping cost will be deducted from your refund.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>4. Refund or Exchange Options</h2>
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Refund</h3>
                <p>Refunds will be processed to the <strong>original payment method</strong> within 5-7 business days after receiving the returned item.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Exchange</h3>
                <p>You can choose to exchange the returned item for a different size or color, subject to availability.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>5. Customer Communication</h2>
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Confirmation Email</h3>
                <p>After initiating a return, a confirmation email will be sent with all the return details.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Return Status Tracking</h3>
                <p>Track the status of your return through your account dashboard under the "Returns" section.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>6. Inspection and Processing Time</h2>
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Processing Time</h3>
                <p>Returns are processed within <strong>3-5 business days</strong> after we receive the item.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Inspection Details</h3>
                <p>All returned items are inspected to ensure they meet our return policy criteria before a refund or exchange is issued.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>7. Contact Information</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our customer support:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Email: support@yourecommerce.com</li>
                <li>Phone: (123) 456-7890</li>
                <li>Live Chat: Available 24/7 on our website</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>8. Legal and Tax Considerations</h2>
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Tax Refunds</h3>
                <p>Applicable taxes paid will be refunded along with the product amount.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="subsection">
                <h3>Compliance</h3>
                <p>Our return policy complies with all relevant consumer protection laws and regulations.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2024 YourEcommerce. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
